OL,6,
OL,7,GThere was an awkward moment at the
OL,8,Gstart of the weather segment on the BBC
OL,9,GNews at One today, when a studio guest
OL,10,Ggot in the way of the camera shot.
OL,12,
OL,13,FEconomics correspondent Andy Verity was
OL,14,Fseated at the Studio E desk for a brief
OL,15,Fdiscussion with presenter Jane Hill on
OL,16,Fthe programme's final story.
OL,18,
OL,19,FDiscussion complete and it was time to
OL,20,Fpop across to the catwalk for the
OL,21,Fweather, with Tomasz Schafernaker.
