OL,6,
OL,7,FAs usual, when we transition to the
OL,8,Fweather segment, we get a wide shot of
OL,9,Fthe studio. But something's not quite
OL,10,Fright.
OL,12,
OL,13,FThe floor manager is seen waving
OL,14,Ffrantically to catch Andy Verity's
OL,15,Fattention. Presumably she's been
OL,16,Finformed by the director that Andy is
OL,17,Fobstructing the camera shot of the
OL,18,Fweather presenter.
